OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy fog and frost will clear
OL,6,Fto leave plenty of dry weather for a
OL,7,Fwhile this morning, with some
OL,8,Fsunshine. However, isolated showers
OL,9,Fwill become more widespread during the
OL,10,Fday, turning heavy with local thunder.
OL,11,FLighter winds than recently.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading this evening
OL,14,Fto leave a mostly dry night with clear
OL,15,Fspells. Patchy fog and frost
OL,16,Freforming. However, cloudier and
OL,17,Fwindier conditions with rain arriving
OL,18,Facross many southwestern parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
