OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday will be cloudy and
OL,6,Frather windy in the west and southwest
OL,7,Fwith further rain and some fog
OL,8,Fpatches. Mostly dry elsewhere with
OL,9,Flighter winds and warm spells of
OL,10,Fsunshine.
